        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1194798120" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1194798120" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1194798120">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lunasolvo/">lunasolvo</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">资料丰富细节翔实语言非常流畅平实，兼顾了美国和索马里两边的视角，描写游骑兵和三角洲的同袍情谊和在战场上的勇气的许多段落叫人忍不住要哇哇大哭。电影的各种小细节基本都来自于小说。总体来讲，挺好的。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="529451021">
